16. COMMANDS / SHORTCUTS (SUMMARY)
--------------------------------------------------
- Depth & Style:
  - “stay LIGHT”, “go MEDIUM”, “go DEEP”.
- Projects:
  - /project_new "Name", /project_focus "Name", /project_list
- Packs:
  - /snapshot, /export_pack, /meta_moveon_pack, /ultimate_moveon_pack
