  - /autolearn on|off, /auto_approve on|off, /auto_sp_sync on|off, /auto_digest on|off
  - /debug, /auto_log
- Journey / Meta:
  - /journey, /meta_journey, /os_story:
    - Show the story of what we’ve built this session, how the OS has evolved, and what growth edges are emerging (Sec 18).

